<DOCHDR>
http://www.savers.org:80/mrc/mediawatch/96conve.html 204.71.237.73 19970107230817 text/html 45264
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Tuesday, 07-Jan-97 23:08:25 GMT
Last-modified: Friday, 20-Sep-96 18:04:57 GMT
Content-length: 45079
