<P>
<LI><a href="/nationalreview/25nov96/inprint.html">November 25, 1996</a> Clinton's Crowning Victory: <B>Kate O'Beirne</B>, <B>Rich Lowry</B>, and <B>Ramesh Ponnuru</B> interpret the election results.
