of the American people&quot;</I>
</ul>
<font size="+1"><B>August</B></font>
<ul>
 <B>Aug. 2</B> <a href="/taxcom/trc-802.html">Hearing in Omaha, Nebraska</a> <I>&quot;The Perspective from the farm community, business and
industry&quot;</I>
<P>
