<DOCHDR>
http://www.savers.org:80/mrc/cyberalert/cyb1217.html 204.71.237.73 19970107233446 text/html 13560
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Tuesday, 07-Jan-97 23:35:00 GMT
Last-modified: Tuesday, 17-Dec-96 16:27:35 GMT
